author: jonesde
msg: Added some comments about feature application types to clear up some confusion and misconceptions

author: eyang
msg: CHUKWA-26.  * DemuxManager, ArchiveManager and PostProcessorManager are now a single daemon process each.
* Each one working independently from others, as soon as something is available.
* Start-data-processor is now using those new daemons instead of pocessSink.sh
* Daily will process a daily compaction only when all hourly would have been done.
* Demux is now able to send NSCA commands to Nagios. (Jerome Boulon via Eric Yang)

author: jacopoc
msg: A bunch of fixes and enhancements to the new widget renderers based on Freemarker macros.
Converted to new technology the xsl-fo renderer and view handler.

Better handling of platform dependent templates included in screens: the proper one is now choosen according to the name of the renderer; the name is returned by a new method of the widget renderer interface.
